<plot>Jacob Lewis, a painter, struggles greatly after losing his wife to a fatal car accident two years ago. Trying to cope with his pain, he spends his time in seclusion and begins a new relationship with a mysterious woman, burying himself in his work and rarely leaving his studio. This woman becomes his drug of choice and his art reflects this female obsession. Will he overcome this obsession or continue to fall further from reality?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?539007</url></doc>
